title: Space Island One - season 2
description:
This is the complete second season of "Space Island One".  Sorry, not the best copies (sometimes dark or out of sync) but better than nothing if you can't find it elsewhere.  Made from old VCR tapes from the late nineties, shown on the Space channel in Canada.  Videotape degrades over time.
 <a href="
http://io9.com/5347065/the-top-100-science-fictionfantasy-shows-41-through-50" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://io9.com/5347065/the-top-100-science-fictionfantasy-shows-41-through-50</a>
Number 41 on the Top 100 Best Science Fiction Shows of All Time list.  Should be much higher up in my opinion.  They describe it as: "the best science fiction show you've never heard of".
